Package org.frogger.gameController

Class HighScorePageController

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.frogger.gameController.HighScorePageController
  • public class HighScorePageController
extends java.lang.Object

    HighScorePageController

    This class represents a controller to control the HighScorePage Model, which includes buttons allowing user interaction and handles user input events.

    This class integrates the methods to allow user interaction. The top-10 high scores with corresponding players' names will be shown on the game board.
